Package stock.model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IPortfolio
    This interface describes a single portfolio and operations that can be performed by a portfolio.
    IPortfolioManagerModel
    This interface represents the model of this program.
    IStock
    This interface represents a single stock.
    PersistentPortfolioManagerModel
    This interface is an enhanced version of IPortfolioManagerModel.
    PersistPortfolioJSON
    The interface that handles the serializing and deserializing of portfolio objects.
    PersistStrategyJSON
    The interface that handles the serializing and deserializing of portfolio objects.
    Strategy
    An interface that facilitates creation of new high level investment strategies that can be applied on a portfolio.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DollarCostStrategy
    A Strategy class that implements dollar cost averaging.
    PersistPortfolioJSONImpl
    Implements the persisting of Portfolio object into a JSON and convert it back.
    PersistStrategyJSONImpl
    Implements the persisting of Strategy object into a JSON and convert it back.
    PortfolioImpl
    The class that implements a Portfolio.
    PortfolioManagerModel
    A class that implements the PortfolioManagerModel.
    RegularStrategy
    A Strategy class that implements a regular investment strategy of buying one stock at a given amount on a given day.
    StockAdapter
    The adapter class for converting Stock interface objects into their JSON and vice versa.
    StockImpl
